<h1 class="text-center"> Welcome to VaiLocal! </h1>

<h5 class="text-center">VaiLocal is a hyper-local jobs board and social network for high school and college students. Apart from listing jobs on our site, we also seek to connect high schoolers who have questions about college, internships, scholarships, athletics recruiting, and more on a forum with college students and adults who can offer guidance. </h5>

<hr>

<h4 class="text-center">Create your account today!</h4>

<div class="text-center">
<table border="1">
<form action="/insert_user" method="post" class = "text-center form-horizontal" enctype = "multipart/form-data" >

  <div>
    <label for="email_box">Email</label>
    <input id="email_box" name="query_email" placeholder="Choose an email..." type="text">
  </div>
                 
  <div>
    <label for="first_name_box">First name</label>
    <input type="text" id="first_name_box" name="query_first_name">
  </div>
         
  <div>
    <label for="last_name_box">Last name</label>
    <input type="text" id="last_name_box" name="query_last_name">
  </div>
         
         
  <div>
    <label for="school_name_box">School name</label>
    <input type="text" id="school_name_box" name="query_school_name" placeholder = "Your current school">
  </div>
    
  <div>
    <label for="password_box">Password</label>
    <input id="password_box" name="query_password" placeholder="Choose a password..." type="password">
  </div>

  <div>
    <label for="password_confirmation_box">Password Confirmation</label>
    <input id="password_confirmation_box" name="query_password_confirmation" placeholder="Confirm your password..." type="password">
  </div>

  <button class = "v-button">
    Sign up
  </button>
</form>
</table>
</div>

<hr>

<p class="text-center">
  Or, <a href="/user_sign_in">Sign in</a> instead.
</p>
